OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with some mostly light
OL,6,Frain at times, though with some drier
OL,7,Fspells too. Some heavier rain will
OL,8,Freach the west coast by evening, with
OL,9,Fstrong to gale southerly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FHeavy rain will sweep east
OL,12,Facross the region this evening
OL,13,Faccompanied by strong to gale south or
OL,14,Fsouthwest winds. Clearer for a time
OL,15,Ftonight then frequent blustery showers
OL,16,Fsetting in.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
