OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA cloudy start with
OL,6,Ffrequent blustery showers and gale
OL,7,Fforce winds. A brighter afternoon with
OL,8,Fsome sunny intervals but still some
OL,9,Fshowers. Winds slowly easing.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FHeavy
OL,12,Frain then blustery showers on
OL,13,FThursday, gales. Colder with sunshine
OL,14,Fand showers on Friday, snow on high
OL,15,Fground. Remaining showery on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
